        {
            "title": "黑期低水逾10點 重磅港股ADR中金融股造好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時12分升1點，報25912點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報25904點，較香港上日現貨收市低23點或0.09%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣614.1元，較上日香港收市低5.43元或0.88%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣153.2元，較上日香港收市低1.57元或1.02%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合港幣102.5元，較上日香港收市低1.32元或1.28%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合港幣114.4元，較上日香港收市低0.39元或0.34%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合港幣40.1元，較上日香港收市低0.01元或0.03%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合港幣109.8元，較上日香港收市高2.19元或2.04%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合港幣81.1元，較上日香港收市高0.42元或0.53%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣415.8元，較上日香港收市高2.61元或0.63%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合港幣57.2元，較上日香港收市低0.18元或0.32%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合港幣8.2元，較上日香港收市高0.01元或0.09%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報25924點，跌7點，較上日恒指收市25928點，低水4點。科指期貨夜市收報5595點，較上日科指收市低水23點；國指期貨夜市收報9150點，較上日國指收市低水15點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15460383-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be10%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e4%b8%ad%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e8%82%a1%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-27 08:20:36",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英法德股市高收近1%或以上　英國銀行股造好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲股市升近1%或以上，憧憬美國下月持續減息，提振全球風險偏好。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英法股市連升兩日，英國富時100指數曾升穿9700點，收市報9691點，升82點，升幅0.85%，創近兩星期新高。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國財政大臣李韻晴公布預算案，大規模加稅，但沒有對銀行加徵新稅。銀行股造好，滙控升逾1%，萊斯銀行升逾3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數收報8096點，升70點，升幅近0.9%，創逾1星期高位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數收報23726點，升261點，升幅1.1%，連升3日，創近兩星期新高。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15460232-%e8%8b%b1%e6%b3%95%e5%be%b7%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6%e8%bf%911%e6%88%96%e4%bb%a5%e4%b8%8a%e3%80%80%e8%8b%b1%e5%9c%8b%e9%8a%80%e8%a1%8c%e8%82%a1%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_Germany_Trump_Tariffs_25099406378758-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-27 08:20:38",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美股四連升　道指高收314點　晶片股造好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股在感恩節假期前升勢持續，連續4日高收，創約兩星期新高。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250124_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250124_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">聯儲局褐皮書指出，美國經濟活動變化不大，但政府停擺抑制多個地區需求，亦有約一半地區就業轉弱。另外，美國上星期新申領失業救濟人數減至21.6萬人，創7個月新低，但未有改變下月減息預期。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/USEco_1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/USEco_1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯指數最多升近460點，升穿47500點，收市報47427點，升314點，升幅約0.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標普500指數收報6812點，升46點，升幅約0.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數收報23214點，升189點，升幅逾0.8%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Nvidia反彈逾1%，其他晶片股亦造好，英特爾、博通、AMD升近3%至近4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">蘋果再創收市新高，Alphabet回吐1%，Meta亦偏軟。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15460206-%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a1%e5%9b%9b%e9%80%a3%e5%8d%87%e3%80%80%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6314%e9%bb%9e%e3%80%80%e6%99%b6%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250802_GL_source-AP_WallSt_02.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-27 08:20:41",
